dialogue: Hey, what's the deal with you?

Aren't you supposed to be way more cheerful than this? [color=#b38b2b]Darling[/color]
described you that way, at least.
... I just don't feel like it.
... I have to guard the door to [color=#b38b2b]Wonderland[/color].

Do you know why [color=#b38b2b]Wonderland[/color] is destabilizing? Are we going to
die? Have you seen any bad guys come out?

Don't you remember the [color=#b38b2b]Piper[/color]? You two used to be best
friends... He's out of control, [color=#b38b2b]A5[/color]... It's because of the [color=#e1ec43]Phantasia[/color].
It's driving him totally mad.
What's the [color=#e1ec43]Phantasia[/color]? Is that another bad guy?

I hardly remember who I am, how could I help? Why can’t
anyone else do this, I’m just- I’m me!

If you can snap him out of this, he must be able to return your
memories.
You really think I can do that?
... I'll figure this out, somehow. Thank you for helping me.
